# Runtime-generated company-uploaded corpora (Phase 3 retrieval package).
# These are user-uploaded documents + derived chunk/embedding indices —
# never source, never part of the tracked demo dataset. Keep the folder
# itself tracked (via this file + .gitkeep) so the app has somewhere to
# write when RETRIEVAL_ENABLED=1, without committing anyone's uploads.
*
!.gitignore
!.gitkeep
